WEBVTT

00:01:29.670 --> 00:01:34.930
[Our Dazzling Days]

00:01:35.289 --> 00:01:37.800
[Episode 20]

00:01:52.430 --> 00:01:53.509
We made it!

00:01:53.660 --> 00:01:54.509
Awesome!

00:01:55.670 --> 00:01:56.530
What happened?

00:01:57.509 --> 00:01:58.920
All the bugs have been fixed.

00:01:58.920 --> 00:02:00.350
The closed beta test was a huge success.

00:02:00.350 --> 00:02:01.120
So we can launch it now?

00:02:01.120 --> 00:02:02.320
Whenever you want to.

00:02:06.080 --> 00:02:07.280
I need to tell Mr. Xue!

00:02:12.910 --> 00:02:15.160
Mr. Xue,
the closed beta test was a success.

00:02:15.160 --> 00:02:16.760
It can be launched right now!

00:02:18.470 --> 00:02:19.870
No problem, of course!

00:02:20.150 --> 00:02:21.079
Let's go for it!

00:02:29.800 --> 00:02:30.800
Going for a walk?

00:02:33.400 --> 00:02:34.060
Mr. Zhuang!

00:02:34.430 --> 00:02:35.150
Hey, Xia.

00:02:35.170 --> 00:02:36.800
Where are you going with that stuff?

00:02:36.800 --> 00:02:38.600
I'm going to play chess with Sun.

00:02:38.910 --> 00:02:40.750
You got off work this early today?

00:02:40.750 --> 00:02:42.070
Because I had to buy this,

00:02:42.070 --> 00:02:44.750
Caozi cake. It sells out
before my usual working hours end.

00:02:44.750 --> 00:02:46.010
I'm going to pay a visit

00:02:46.150 --> 00:02:47.250
to Xia Lei in Shanghai.

00:02:47.250 --> 00:02:48.250
He loves this cake.

00:02:48.250 --> 00:02:49.800
Shanghai has everything.

00:02:49.829 --> 00:02:51.360
Who cares about Caozi cake?

00:02:51.410 --> 00:02:52.870
But its taste is unique, isn't it?

00:02:52.870 --> 00:02:54.520
This flavor is exclusive
to the East Chemical Factory.

00:02:54.520 --> 00:02:56.380
It can't be bought anywhere else.

00:03:01.490 --> 00:03:01.660
[Xun Fei Tian Xia Network Technology
Co., Ltd.]

00:03:01.660 --> 00:03:02.790
Come on in, Mom, Dad.

00:03:03.230 --> 00:03:03.750
Look.

00:03:04.440 --> 00:03:05.500
This is my company.

00:03:06.180 --> 00:03:07.180
Impressive, huh?

00:03:07.900 --> 00:03:08.900
Yes, very much so.

00:03:11.360 --> 00:03:12.030
Look at the view outside.

00:03:12.030 --> 00:03:12.890
Hello, Mr. Xia.

00:03:13.310 --> 00:03:14.440
It's huge, isn't it?

00:03:14.560 --> 00:03:16.190
It's not all mine.
Two other companies are over there.

00:03:16.190 --> 00:03:17.790
We rent this place with them.

00:03:18.410 --> 00:03:19.380
I mean this whole area.

00:03:19.380 --> 00:03:20.380
Really splendid.

00:03:20.560 --> 00:03:21.710
As I said, we shouldn't have come.

00:03:21.710 --> 00:03:22.400
-They need to work.
-Mr. Xia.

00:03:22.400 --> 00:03:22.960
What's up?

00:03:22.960 --> 00:03:25.220
This document requires your signature.

00:03:27.079 --> 00:03:28.710
Shouldn’t you ask Mr. Fan to sign this?

00:03:28.710 --> 00:03:30.840
Mr. Fan has been absent the entire day.

00:03:38.630 --> 00:03:39.280
All done.

00:03:45.840 --> 00:03:46.840
What's that look?

00:03:47.390 --> 00:03:48.870
This is making me feel awkward.

00:03:48.870 --> 00:03:49.910
Come this way.

00:03:50.680 --> 00:03:51.540
Look at him now.

00:03:56.120 --> 00:03:57.590
This is my office.

00:03:58.400 --> 00:04:00.130
The general manager's office.

00:04:00.190 --> 00:04:02.150
What a beautiful sight outside the window.

00:04:02.150 --> 00:04:03.280
Nice view, isn't it?

00:04:04.360 --> 00:04:04.870
Can I sit...

00:04:04.870 --> 00:04:06.470
Make yourself comfortable.

00:04:07.750 --> 00:04:08.810
Such a great place.

00:04:10.520 --> 00:04:11.980
It's really a great place.

00:04:13.960 --> 00:04:14.690
Not bad, huh?

00:04:16.750 --> 00:04:18.029
At this critical moment,

00:04:18.029 --> 00:04:19.560
he's nowhere to be found.

00:04:20.750 --> 00:04:21.390
Take a seat, Dad.

00:04:21.390 --> 00:04:22.560
What a nice place this is.

00:04:22.560 --> 00:04:24.040
Y-Y-You should get back to work.

00:04:24.040 --> 00:04:25.160
D-Don't let us hold you up.

00:04:25.160 --> 00:04:26.600
We'll sit here for a bit.

00:04:26.600 --> 00:04:27.750
Go do your job now.

00:04:27.750 --> 00:04:28.390
Yes. You go do your thing.

00:04:28.390 --> 00:04:29.240
Off you go!

00:04:29.560 --> 00:04:30.560
But where am I supposed to go?

00:04:30.560 --> 00:04:32.150
T-This is my own office.

00:04:32.750 --> 00:04:33.190
Right.

00:04:33.190 --> 00:04:34.850
He works right in this office.

00:04:34.870 --> 00:04:36.390
Besides,
the company and the network projects

00:04:36.390 --> 00:04:37.770
are on the right track now.

00:04:37.770 --> 00:04:39.300
I'll leave the work to them.

00:04:40.360 --> 00:04:41.270
You are pretty busy yourself.

00:04:41.270 --> 00:04:42.560
You're signing papers one moment,

00:04:42.560 --> 00:04:44.020
and making calls the next.

00:04:44.159 --> 00:04:44.600
I have to say,

00:04:44.600 --> 00:04:47.130
our son looks quite good
when he signs papers.

00:04:48.950 --> 00:04:49.560
Son,

00:04:50.380 --> 00:04:51.670
I was just thinking

00:04:52.560 --> 00:04:54.360
maybe you should cancel
the hotel reservations

00:04:54.360 --> 00:04:55.800
for me and your mom.

00:04:56.040 --> 00:04:57.430
We'll be out for tours during the day,

00:04:57.430 --> 00:04:58.950
and only stay at the hotel for sleep
at night.

00:04:58.950 --> 00:05:00.950
We won't be in the room for much time.

00:05:01.160 --> 00:05:02.190
When I passing by, I noticed

00:05:02.190 --> 00:05:03.900
that big comfy couch in the open office.

00:05:03.900 --> 00:05:05.450
Your mom can sleep on it at night,

00:05:05.450 --> 00:05:07.180
and I'll just sleep on the floor.

00:05:07.180 --> 00:05:08.270
Don't worry about me.

00:05:08.270 --> 00:05:10.070
I've slept in all sorts of places
as a driver.

00:05:10.070 --> 00:05:12.070
None of them are half as nice as here.

00:05:12.430 --> 00:05:13.720
-Just cancel the bookings.
-You won't stay at the hotel?

00:05:13.720 --> 00:05:15.320
No, I won't. It's confirmed.

00:05:15.750 --> 00:05:16.800
But even in that case,

00:05:16.800 --> 00:05:18.680
I can't get a refund.

00:05:18.910 --> 00:05:20.150
Fine. Don't stay at the hotel then.

00:05:20.150 --> 00:05:21.310
No, wait a second.

00:05:22.000 --> 00:05:23.390
Even if the bookings are cancelled,

00:05:23.390 --> 00:05:24.560
you won't get a refund?

00:05:24.560 --> 00:05:27.070
Stop it. You're giving him wrong advice.

00:05:27.270 --> 00:05:29.000
Our son's career is going so well.

00:05:29.000 --> 00:05:30.040
Don't worry at all.

00:05:30.040 --> 00:05:31.360
Stay at the hotel as planned.

00:05:31.360 --> 00:05:32.040
-Silly you.
-Mom's right.

00:05:32.040 --> 00:05:33.510
Just relax and stay at the hotel.

00:05:33.510 --> 00:05:34.480
S-Since you won't get a refund,

00:05:34.480 --> 00:05:35.900
don't c-cancel the bookings then.

00:05:35.900 --> 00:05:36.960
Or it'll be a waste.

00:05:37.120 --> 00:05:37.760
Oh, right.

00:05:39.800 --> 00:05:41.860
I need to discuss something with you.

00:05:42.430 --> 00:05:44.000
Upon receiving my bonus
at the end of the year,

00:05:44.000 --> 00:05:45.930
I'm going to place the down payment

00:05:46.310 --> 00:05:47.270
for a new apartment.

00:05:47.270 --> 00:05:48.190
Then I'll have you two

00:05:48.190 --> 00:05:50.390
move here from the East Chemical Plant.

00:05:50.870 --> 00:05:52.390
Uncle Yan's living here too, isn't he?

00:05:52.390 --> 00:05:53.950
You can keep each other company,

00:05:53.950 --> 00:05:55.120
like going out for a walk

00:05:55.120 --> 00:05:55.950
or a meal,

00:05:55.950 --> 00:05:57.480
and playing cards, right?

00:05:57.570 --> 00:05:58.480
Sounds good, Son.

00:05:58.480 --> 00:06:00.430
-You're buying an apartment?
-Your words

00:06:00.430 --> 00:06:01.750
have really...

00:06:01.750 --> 00:06:03.120
warmed my heart.

00:06:03.390 --> 00:06:04.680
But we won't move here.

00:06:04.680 --> 00:06:05.240
You see,

00:06:05.240 --> 00:06:06.700
apartments are expensive in Shanghai,
aren't they?

00:06:06.700 --> 00:06:08.070
I'm telling you, your dad...

00:06:08.070 --> 00:06:10.070
He drives a taxi every day
and makes money.

00:06:10.070 --> 00:06:11.000
All his earnings will be yours.

00:06:11.000 --> 00:06:11.480
That's right.

00:06:11.480 --> 00:06:12.750
Plus, m-my secret savings

00:06:12.750 --> 00:06:13.600
will be yours too.

00:06:13.600 --> 00:06:15.070
We're living happily
at the East Chemical Plant.

00:06:15.070 --> 00:06:17.560
We can't live with you
after you get married, right?

00:06:17.560 --> 00:06:18.160
Right.

00:06:18.160 --> 00:06:19.690
T-Then when the time comes,

00:06:19.800 --> 00:06:21.480
let's move to the same compound.

00:06:21.480 --> 00:06:22.750
We'll live in the same compound.

00:06:22.750 --> 00:06:23.870
How much money do you make, Son?

00:06:23.870 --> 00:06:24.630
-Isn't it nice?
-That means

00:06:24.630 --> 00:06:25.630
to buy two apartments.

00:06:25.630 --> 00:06:27.230
He needs to answer the phone.

00:06:29.040 --> 00:06:30.040
Mr. Fan,

00:06:31.190 --> 00:06:32.630
what's with you?

00:06:33.070 --> 00:06:35.670
Why is it so hard for my parents
to meet with you?

00:06:35.950 --> 00:06:36.830
Sorry, Lei.

00:06:37.000 --> 00:06:38.560
What are you sorry for?

00:06:38.670 --> 00:06:40.580
Three drinks await you as punishment
when we eat tonight.

00:06:40.580 --> 00:06:42.180
Let's have dinner together.

00:06:42.390 --> 00:06:44.530
Fan He embezzled money
from Jiangnan Machinery Plant.

00:06:44.530 --> 00:06:45.360
He has fled.

00:06:47.430 --> 00:06:48.240
I'll take this call outside.

00:06:48.240 --> 00:06:49.970
-Go ahead.
-Just do your thing.

00:06:50.120 --> 00:06:51.950
He's even closing the door.

00:06:52.270 --> 00:06:53.240
What do you mean? Say it again.

00:06:53.240 --> 00:06:54.100
I didn't get it.

00:06:54.460 --> 00:06:56.870
Jiangnan Machinery Plant
is my family business.

00:06:56.870 --> 00:06:59.430
Now creditors are at my door,
and banks are calling in loans.

00:06:59.430 --> 00:07:01.120
All I can do
is sell my websites and company

00:07:01.120 --> 00:07:03.310
to raise funds so I can pay off the loans.

00:07:03.310 --> 00:07:04.870
I'm a shareholder of this company.

00:07:04.870 --> 00:07:05.830
You can't sell it as you please.

00:07:05.830 --> 00:07:07.180
Have you asked for my consent?

00:07:07.180 --> 00:07:08.430
Are we good friends or not?

00:07:08.430 --> 00:07:10.830
Lei, I have to make up the shortfall.

00:07:10.830 --> 00:07:12.310
I can't let the crisis continue.

00:07:12.310 --> 00:07:12.800
I'm sorry.

00:07:12.800 --> 00:07:13.240
"Sorry"?

00:07:13.240 --> 00:07:14.700
To hell with your apology!

00:07:14.800 --> 00:07:15.920
I've given my all to this company.

00:07:15.920 --> 00:07:18.180
How can it be sold
just because you say so?

00:07:18.270 --> 00:07:20.000
I've also dedicated a lot to it.

00:07:20.120 --> 00:07:22.040
I'll transfer the value of company shares
and dividends

00:07:22.040 --> 00:07:23.500
from the internet projects
to Jiangnan Machinery Plant.

00:07:23.500 --> 00:07:25.520
I promise to pay you back,
including interest.

00:07:25.520 --> 00:07:27.920
Besides,
you have to leave the company now,

00:07:28.250 --> 00:07:29.600
since I've sold all your equity.

00:07:29.600 --> 00:07:30.240
Where are you?

00:07:30.240 --> 00:07:31.570
I-I-I'll come meet you right now.

00:07:31.570 --> 00:07:32.400
Don't bother.

00:07:33.120 --> 00:07:34.000
All that said,

00:07:35.000 --> 00:07:35.870
I'm sorry.

00:07:44.600 --> 00:07:45.390
Hello.

00:07:45.840 --> 00:07:46.520
Hello.

00:07:46.750 --> 00:07:48.810
May I talk to the personnel in charge?

00:07:52.180 --> 00:07:53.810
You're the general manager,

00:07:53.870 --> 00:07:54.930
Mr. Xia Lei, right?

00:07:55.000 --> 00:07:55.590
Yes.

00:07:56.220 --> 00:07:59.240
I am the business representative
for Helian Zongheng Group.

00:07:59.240 --> 00:08:01.120
I'm here to handle

00:08:01.120 --> 00:08:02.800
the handover procedures

00:08:02.800 --> 00:08:04.240
on behalf of the group.

00:08:05.920 --> 00:08:07.310
I had doubts

00:08:07.310 --> 00:08:08.960
when Lei first started his own business.

00:08:08.960 --> 00:08:11.550
He hadn't finished school by then.

00:08:11.580 --> 00:08:13.190
One should never try to run

00:08:13.190 --> 00:08:14.510
before learning to walk.

00:08:14.510 --> 00:08:15.750
He was too young at that time,

00:08:15.750 --> 00:08:16.230
wasn't he?

00:08:16.230 --> 00:08:17.480
Nonetheless, Lei did do a good job

00:08:17.480 --> 00:08:19.210
running the previous company.

00:08:19.570 --> 00:08:21.940
Our son is quite capable, in a sense.

00:08:22.160 --> 00:08:23.040
Listen,

00:08:23.040 --> 00:08:24.440
-kids...
-Yan, sit here.

00:08:25.750 --> 00:08:28.560
They tumble.
That happens, and it doesn't matter.

00:08:28.680 --> 00:08:29.190
Right?

00:08:30.500 --> 00:08:31.730
For them,

00:08:31.760 --> 00:08:34.049
lessons learned are assets gained.

00:08:34.320 --> 00:08:35.840
Yes, I think you're right.

00:08:36.630 --> 00:08:38.240
He told us he still wants to stay

00:08:38.240 --> 00:08:39.120
in Shanghai.

00:08:40.330 --> 00:08:41.890
That's the right choice.

00:08:42.299 --> 00:08:43.460
It's a good thing.

00:08:44.030 --> 00:08:45.510
When you get back, tell Lei

00:08:46.140 --> 00:08:47.960
that if he runs into difficulties,

00:08:47.960 --> 00:08:49.200
as long as it's within my capability...

00:08:49.200 --> 00:08:50.200
-Yeah.
-Right?

00:08:50.200 --> 00:08:51.510
I'll do everything to help.

00:08:51.510 --> 00:08:51.960
Yeah.

00:08:53.070 --> 00:08:54.720
Thank you, Chief Engineer Yan, Mrs. Yan.

00:08:54.720 --> 00:08:56.750
Please. Drop the formalities.

00:08:56.750 --> 00:08:59.080
We've been friends for years, haven't we?

00:08:59.440 --> 00:09:01.370
What are your plans for the future?

00:09:01.940 --> 00:09:04.340
I'm done with starting businesses anyway.

00:09:04.390 --> 00:09:06.390
I plan to send out my resume

00:09:06.420 --> 00:09:07.300
and find a job.

00:09:07.960 --> 00:09:09.230
How about I ask my dad to...

00:09:09.230 --> 00:09:11.490
I've already troubled Uncle Yan enough.

00:09:11.700 --> 00:09:13.840
Now, I have my eyes
on a foreign-invested company.

00:09:13.840 --> 00:09:15.240
Meng Ge is working there.

00:09:15.550 --> 00:09:17.150
You'll land the job you want.

00:09:17.750 --> 00:09:19.020
Whatever decisions you make,

00:09:19.020 --> 00:09:20.420
we'll always support you

00:09:20.790 --> 00:09:22.660
and firmly believe

00:09:22.690 --> 00:09:24.490
that a bright future awaits you.

00:09:25.480 --> 00:09:26.720
Thank you then.

00:09:28.150 --> 00:09:29.960
How is your visa coming along?

00:09:29.960 --> 00:09:30.910
It's all done.

00:09:31.160 --> 00:09:33.070
I'm going to France early next month.

00:09:33.070 --> 00:09:33.980
Then I wish you,

00:09:34.320 --> 00:09:36.810
our captain, success in

00:09:36.840 --> 00:09:38.440
exploring new territories.

00:09:38.910 --> 00:09:41.550
Thanks.
We're all heading for a fresh start,

00:09:41.550 --> 00:09:43.550
a particularly good new beginning,

00:09:43.790 --> 00:09:44.920
including Xiaoman.

00:09:46.150 --> 00:09:47.550
Yes, including Xiaoman.

00:09:51.430 --> 00:09:53.030
Have you thought it through?

00:09:56.670 --> 00:09:59.480
Xiaodan will only be away for two years.

00:10:00.590 --> 00:10:01.840
Two years pass quickly

00:10:01.840 --> 00:10:03.010
just like a flash.

00:10:04.930 --> 00:10:08.220
Back then, you told me

00:10:08.870 --> 00:10:11.400
to try to align with others.

00:10:13.010 --> 00:10:15.670
But I was too silly
to understand what you meant.

00:10:15.870 --> 00:10:18.870
See, during the four years
Xiaodan spent in Shanghai,

00:10:20.240 --> 00:10:21.910
I felt the gap between us was getting

00:10:21.910 --> 00:10:23.370
bigger and bigger, driving us

00:10:23.370 --> 00:10:25.510
further and further away from each other.

00:10:25.510 --> 00:10:27.750
Now, she's heading to France,

00:10:28.410 --> 00:10:29.670
a remote foreign land.

00:10:30.870 --> 00:10:31.480
I-If I

00:10:32.130 --> 00:10:33.240
don't catch up with her,

00:10:33.240 --> 00:10:36.300
I won't even understanding
what she says in the future.

00:10:39.790 --> 00:10:42.120
I've tried to persuade you several times.

00:10:42.360 --> 00:10:43.880
But there's no way you can stop me.

00:10:43.880 --> 00:10:44.610
True enough.

00:10:45.790 --> 00:10:48.450
You've been into Xiaodan
since you were little.

00:10:50.430 --> 00:10:51.760
It's been so many years.

00:10:52.260 --> 00:10:53.460
I can't give up on her.

00:10:53.870 --> 00:10:55.910
I truly want to maintain my relationship
with her.

00:10:55.910 --> 00:10:57.570
See, she has made so many trips

00:10:58.120 --> 00:10:59.790
back and forth to visit me.

00:11:00.430 --> 00:11:02.550
I can't let her be the only one trying.

00:11:02.570 --> 00:11:05.360
I also need to make a gesture

00:11:05.450 --> 00:11:06.710
and put in some effort.

00:11:11.140 --> 00:11:11.940
Take my money.

00:11:12.790 --> 00:11:14.100
Mentor, what are you doing? Quick,

00:11:14.100 --> 00:11:15.560
get it back. Don't do this.

00:11:16.510 --> 00:11:17.670
Why refuse my help at all?

00:11:17.670 --> 00:11:19.270
My wife and I don't need this money.

00:11:19.270 --> 00:11:20.790
What should the two of us
even spend it on?

00:11:20.790 --> 00:11:22.200
But even though you're at home with her,

00:11:22.200 --> 00:11:24.000
you need to have some savings, right?

00:11:24.000 --> 00:11:26.120
Besides,
it's not like I don't have any money.

00:11:26.120 --> 00:11:27.780
I have earned some, haven't I?

00:11:28.230 --> 00:11:31.110
You've kept me fed for years.

00:11:31.400 --> 00:11:32.350
What will it make me look like

00:11:32.350 --> 00:11:33.680
if I take money from you?

00:11:34.190 --> 00:11:35.240
Mentor, k-keep this money.

00:11:35.240 --> 00:11:37.640
If I really have an emergency
in the future,

00:11:37.750 --> 00:11:39.120
I-I'll ask you for help—

00:11:39.120 --> 00:11:40.920
that won't make me feel awkward.

00:11:44.200 --> 00:11:45.000
Xiaoman,

00:11:47.030 --> 00:11:47.910
my wife and I

00:11:49.240 --> 00:11:50.840
regard you as our only child.

00:11:53.730 --> 00:11:54.940
What's ours is yours.

00:11:57.560 --> 00:11:58.320
Got it.

00:12:08.430 --> 00:12:11.160
[France, 2002]

00:12:38.840 --> 00:12:40.100
Your trip to France...

00:12:40.240 --> 00:12:41.040
won't happen.

00:12:41.550 --> 00:12:42.120
Why?

00:12:42.380 --> 00:12:45.640
A friend of mine wrote out
a list of application materials.

00:12:46.870 --> 00:12:48.130
These many materials?

00:12:48.440 --> 00:12:49.500
Look further down.

00:12:50.060 --> 00:12:52.060
The amount for the proof of deposit.

00:12:52.080 --> 00:12:54.190
W-Where am I supposed
to get this much money?

00:12:54.190 --> 00:12:56.240
Even if we sell our clothing store

00:12:57.510 --> 00:12:59.840
and get our money back
from the dance hall,

00:13:00.520 --> 00:13:02.250
it'll still be far from enough.

00:13:03.150 --> 00:13:04.610
Is there no other solution?

00:13:04.610 --> 00:13:06.000
Does going out have to be this hard?

00:13:06.000 --> 00:13:07.460
Going out isn't a problem,

00:13:07.910 --> 00:13:09.120
but going abroad is.

00:13:09.840 --> 00:13:11.750
That said, I've come up with an idea.

00:13:11.750 --> 00:13:13.210
My aunt's in Japan, right?

00:13:13.840 --> 00:13:15.840
You can first work in Japan for a year

00:13:15.930 --> 00:13:16.870
to earn quick money.

00:13:16.870 --> 00:13:17.910
By the time you save up enough money,

00:13:17.910 --> 00:13:19.630
and have an international travel record,

00:13:19.630 --> 00:13:21.120
you'll gain access to France easily.

00:13:21.120 --> 00:13:22.390
What? Is it easy to get a visa to Japan?

00:13:22.390 --> 00:13:24.550
Many people from the Northeast
dwell in Japan now.

00:13:24.550 --> 00:13:25.750
There are agents
that handle this type of visa.

00:13:25.750 --> 00:13:27.350
So now I have to take a detour.

00:13:30.240 --> 00:13:31.350
Stop hesitating.
Will you go for it or what?

00:13:31.350 --> 00:13:32.350
Fine, yes, I will.

00:13:39.750 --> 00:13:40.320
These clothes...

00:13:40.320 --> 00:13:42.080
weren't washed at all. They stink.

00:13:42.080 --> 00:13:43.840
Why did you put them in the closet at all?

00:13:43.840 --> 00:13:45.980
I did wash them.
They just got damp in that humid corner.

00:13:45.980 --> 00:13:47.100
They're soggy.

00:13:47.130 --> 00:13:48.180
So soggy.

00:13:52.120 --> 00:13:54.380
You're only bringing these few clothes?

00:13:54.700 --> 00:13:56.440
Planning to buy new ones
when you get there?

00:13:56.440 --> 00:13:57.510
Won't that be costly?

00:13:57.510 --> 00:13:58.240
Grab two more outfits.

00:13:58.240 --> 00:13:59.470
I'll wash these often.
They're enough for me.

00:13:59.470 --> 00:14:00.600
Just pack some more.

00:14:00.950 --> 00:14:02.590
Fine then.

00:14:08.390 --> 00:14:09.600
Let me add...

00:14:12.510 --> 00:14:13.670
a jacket.

00:14:14.480 --> 00:14:16.320
My wife dried some vegetables for you.

00:14:16.320 --> 00:14:17.200
I'll put them in the suitcase too.

00:14:17.200 --> 00:14:17.900
Okay.

00:14:18.120 --> 00:14:19.520
They are in the top layer.

00:14:19.910 --> 00:14:21.110
Remember to eat them.

00:14:21.150 --> 00:14:22.420
Share with others
if you can't finish this much.

00:14:22.420 --> 00:14:23.440
Bond with those around you.

00:14:23.440 --> 00:14:24.150
I got it.

00:14:24.690 --> 00:14:25.940
Understood.

00:14:26.080 --> 00:14:27.870
Hearing about your departure,
my wife couldn't bring herself to come.

00:14:27.870 --> 00:14:29.070
She's crying at home.

00:14:29.390 --> 00:14:31.320
Gosh. Why even cry?

00:14:31.450 --> 00:14:33.310
What kind of junk have you packed?

00:14:34.800 --> 00:14:37.890
Look, so many people have gone abroad
these days.

00:14:38.550 --> 00:14:39.600
They're all faring well.

00:14:39.600 --> 00:14:40.860
How am I any different?

00:14:41.120 --> 00:14:42.580
How are you any different?

00:14:43.150 --> 00:14:43.840
Don't you know

00:14:43.840 --> 00:14:45.640
the difference, Zhang Xiaoman?

00:14:46.600 --> 00:14:47.600
Have you ever traveled?

00:14:47.600 --> 00:14:48.960
You've never even been anywhere far away.

00:14:48.960 --> 00:14:50.690
But now you're heading to a foreign land.

00:14:50.690 --> 00:14:51.890
What a long distance.

00:14:52.960 --> 00:14:53.960
If you need to get something done

00:14:53.960 --> 00:14:54.870
in that unfamiliar place,

00:14:54.870 --> 00:14:55.530
you will...

00:14:55.630 --> 00:14:57.080
Just thinking about it already worries me

00:14:57.080 --> 00:14:58.340
and wrenches my heart.

00:14:59.270 --> 00:15:00.030
I'll be fine.

00:15:00.200 --> 00:15:03.030
When I get there, I'll keep my head down,

00:15:04.000 --> 00:15:05.030
work hard,

00:15:05.670 --> 00:15:08.440
and save up some money.

00:15:08.550 --> 00:15:09.870
I-I will come back eventually

00:15:09.870 --> 00:15:11.170
to take care of you and your wife.

00:15:11.170 --> 00:15:12.410
Don't even bother.

00:15:12.840 --> 00:15:13.910
Zhang Xiaoman, forget it.

00:15:13.910 --> 00:15:15.600
My wife and I don't need you
to take care of us.

00:15:15.600 --> 00:15:16.400
Do you hear me?

00:15:16.530 --> 00:15:17.790
We are perfectly fine.

00:15:20.120 --> 00:15:21.580
Just look after yourself.

00:15:22.870 --> 00:15:25.200
Let us know you're safe
when you get there.

00:15:29.750 --> 00:15:33.080
If anything happens, tell me immediately.

00:15:33.760 --> 00:15:34.550
You heard me?

00:15:34.990 --> 00:15:36.060
Yes, I got it.

00:15:45.840 --> 00:15:46.390
Alright.

00:15:46.880 --> 00:15:47.360
Is the packing done?

00:15:47.360 --> 00:15:48.440
Put this in as well.

00:15:56.030 --> 00:15:57.440
Here, the buckle is broken.

00:15:57.440 --> 00:15:59.100
I tied it up with a plastic bag.

00:15:59.860 --> 00:16:02.120
When you reach Japan,

00:16:02.120 --> 00:16:04.380
see if there's a flea market or somewhere

00:16:04.600 --> 00:16:05.530
you can buy a bag.

00:16:06.440 --> 00:16:08.170
Only buy a new one if you have to.

00:16:08.330 --> 00:16:09.990
Got it. I'll have to be frugal.

00:16:17.460 --> 00:16:22.010
[Japan, 2002]

00:16:25.960 --> 00:16:26.770
I'm back!

00:16:29.560 --> 00:16:30.370
Come on in.

00:16:31.320 --> 00:16:32.720
Change your shoes first.

00:16:33.720 --> 00:16:34.780
That pair is yours.

00:16:34.830 --> 00:16:35.600
-T-This pair?
-Yes.

00:16:35.600 --> 00:16:36.090
Okay.

00:16:36.120 --> 00:16:36.980
These slippers

00:16:37.320 --> 00:16:39.250
were prepared especially for you.

00:16:39.390 --> 00:16:40.860
Remember not to wear the wrong ones.

00:16:40.860 --> 00:16:41.310
Okay.

00:16:41.530 --> 00:16:42.560
Our boss likes

00:16:42.590 --> 00:16:43.750
everything to be orderly

00:16:43.750 --> 00:16:45.080
both in life and work.

00:16:46.030 --> 00:16:47.410
Order must be maintained.

00:16:47.410 --> 00:16:47.890
Got it.

00:16:47.910 --> 00:16:49.110
I'll show you around.

00:16:50.250 --> 00:16:51.530
This is the kitchen.

00:16:53.390 --> 00:16:54.250
Spacious, huh?

00:16:54.660 --> 00:16:55.790
This is where we eat,

00:16:56.360 --> 00:16:57.290
the dining room.

00:16:59.000 --> 00:17:00.790
And this is where we sleep.

00:17:02.150 --> 00:17:03.680
The bathroom is over there.

00:17:06.050 --> 00:17:07.970
T-T-This is where we sleep?

00:17:09.280 --> 00:17:10.680
Shouldn't there be a bed?

00:17:11.310 --> 00:17:12.030
Japanese prefer

00:17:12.030 --> 00:17:13.290
sleeping on the floor.

00:17:13.510 --> 00:17:14.560
Before you sleep at night,

00:17:14.560 --> 00:17:16.140
take out the bedding and spread it out.

00:17:16.140 --> 00:17:17.170
When you get up in the morning,

00:17:17.170 --> 00:17:19.569
just fold it, put it away,
and it's perfect.

00:17:19.720 --> 00:17:21.920
The boss's room is far down the hallway.

00:17:22.880 --> 00:17:23.480
Don't go there

00:17:23.480 --> 00:17:25.109
unless the boss

00:17:25.109 --> 00:17:26.640
asks you to.

00:17:26.880 --> 00:17:29.400
S-Shall I go say hello to Madam Zhuang?

00:17:31.250 --> 00:17:33.250
Stop calling her Madam Zhuang.

00:17:33.750 --> 00:17:35.830
I think... you should call her Boss

00:17:35.960 --> 00:17:36.790
like we do.

00:17:37.350 --> 00:17:38.110
She's now in the restaurant.

00:17:38.110 --> 00:17:39.370
We'll go there in a bit.

00:17:40.510 --> 00:17:41.910
So nobody else is at home?

00:17:42.640 --> 00:17:44.830
You announced your return when we arrived
just now.

00:17:44.830 --> 00:17:46.630
I thought someone else was here.

00:17:46.640 --> 00:17:48.550
That's also a Japanese custom.

00:17:48.750 --> 00:17:50.720
After spending a long time here,

00:17:50.720 --> 00:17:52.000
I've taken up that habit too.

00:17:52.000 --> 00:17:52.830
In time,

00:17:52.850 --> 00:17:54.200
you'll get used to it as well.

00:17:54.200 --> 00:17:56.130
I didn't dare to make a sound at all.

00:17:56.410 --> 00:17:57.040
Actually,

00:17:57.550 --> 00:17:59.440
I guess the boss will like the way

00:17:59.440 --> 00:18:00.640
you behaved cautiously just now.

00:18:00.640 --> 00:18:02.440
She enjoys peace and quietness.

00:18:02.960 --> 00:18:04.160
Alright, enough chitchat.

00:18:04.160 --> 00:18:05.480
Leave your luggage here for now.

00:18:05.480 --> 00:18:06.240
Let's go to the restaurant now.

00:18:06.240 --> 00:18:07.030
You can sort your stuff tonight.

00:18:07.030 --> 00:18:07.640
-Got it.
-Okay?

00:18:07.640 --> 00:18:08.200
Okay.

00:18:11.440 --> 00:18:12.200
Boss!

00:18:13.790 --> 00:18:15.570
A dish of twice-cooked pork for Table 7.

00:18:15.570 --> 00:18:16.610
Okay, got it.

00:18:17.880 --> 00:18:18.750
Yun!

00:18:20.110 --> 00:18:22.160
Why is it taking Qu so long
to pick that boy up?

00:18:22.160 --> 00:18:23.310
Call and rush him.

00:18:23.440 --> 00:18:23.960
Okay.

00:18:24.960 --> 00:18:26.030
Here we come!

00:18:29.260 --> 00:18:30.460
She's in the kitchen?

00:18:33.480 --> 00:18:34.160
Boss,

00:18:34.820 --> 00:18:36.010
I brought the boy here.

00:18:36.010 --> 00:18:36.550
Okay.

00:18:39.880 --> 00:18:41.680
Well, ma'am, I...

00:18:41.680 --> 00:18:42.240
Move.

00:18:51.270 --> 00:18:51.880
Ma'am,

00:18:52.310 --> 00:18:55.030
I-I'm Zhuang Sen's classmate.

00:18:55.050 --> 00:18:56.210
Don't call me ma'am.

00:18:56.430 --> 00:18:58.030
Zhuang Sen told me about you.

00:18:59.480 --> 00:19:02.400
Only you at the East Chemical Plant
would hang out with him?

00:19:02.400 --> 00:19:04.600
Yes. We've been close since childhood.

00:19:05.820 --> 00:19:07.750
That's why you two are unreliable.

00:19:08.640 --> 00:19:09.970
I-I'm fairly reliable.

00:19:10.170 --> 00:19:11.330
Have you seen that house?

00:19:11.330 --> 00:19:11.920
Yes, I have.

00:19:11.920 --> 00:19:13.850
You'll share a room with Qu and Guo.

00:19:14.130 --> 00:19:14.810
Yes, I know.

00:19:14.920 --> 00:19:15.850
Thank you, Boss.

00:19:15.960 --> 00:19:16.890
You're welcome.

00:19:17.200 --> 00:19:19.400
The rent will be taken from your salary.

00:19:22.360 --> 00:19:24.640
D-Does the job not cover room and board?

00:19:25.240 --> 00:19:27.030
I provide meals, not housing.

00:19:27.550 --> 00:19:29.660
You can take a day off on every Tuesday.

00:19:29.660 --> 00:19:31.270
You'll get paid on a monthly basis.

00:19:31.270 --> 00:19:31.830
Got it.

00:19:34.080 --> 00:19:35.340
I never withhold wages

00:19:35.680 --> 00:19:36.880
or give pay advances.

00:19:37.000 --> 00:19:37.880
Understood?

00:19:38.320 --> 00:19:39.080
Understood.

00:19:39.960 --> 00:19:41.490
Help out in the kitchen now.

00:19:42.750 --> 00:19:44.210
Qu will tell you what to do.

00:19:44.270 --> 00:19:45.350
Sure. Off I go.

00:19:47.070 --> 00:19:47.920
Be steady!

00:19:51.060 --> 00:19:51.690
Mr. Qu!

00:19:52.420 --> 00:19:53.100
Mr. Qu!

00:19:53.940 --> 00:19:55.400
The boss sent me to help.

00:19:55.400 --> 00:19:56.330
What should I do?

00:19:56.510 --> 00:19:57.310
Oh, you...

00:20:00.240 --> 00:20:01.610
No need to rush.

00:20:05.560 --> 00:20:06.750
Let me introduce you to each other.

00:20:06.750 --> 00:20:07.240
Guo.

00:20:07.710 --> 00:20:09.030
This is Guo, somewhat an apprentice

00:20:09.030 --> 00:20:09.590
of mine.

00:20:10.070 --> 00:20:10.850
This is Xiaoman.

00:20:10.850 --> 00:20:12.650
He just came from the Northeast.

00:20:12.830 --> 00:20:15.400
He's friends with the boss's nephew.

00:20:15.400 --> 00:20:16.790
-Am I saying it right?
-Yes.

00:20:16.790 --> 00:20:18.950
We'll be buddies eating from the same pot
from now on.

00:20:18.950 --> 00:20:20.880
My goodness. You're from the Northeast?

00:20:20.880 --> 00:20:21.770
Yes, I'm from Dalian.

00:20:21.770 --> 00:20:22.560
Listen to that accent.

00:20:22.560 --> 00:20:23.820
Come with me, Xiaoman.

00:20:23.880 --> 00:20:24.750
Listen,

00:20:24.830 --> 00:20:26.400
here's where you'll work.

00:20:26.400 --> 00:20:26.920
Okay.

00:20:27.110 --> 00:20:27.680
That

00:20:27.680 --> 00:20:29.480
is for washing dishes and bowls,

00:20:29.790 --> 00:20:31.110
and that for fruits and vegetables.

00:20:31.110 --> 00:20:31.460
Got it.

00:20:31.460 --> 00:20:32.540
Remember,

00:20:32.880 --> 00:20:34.750
rinse the plates thoroughly
after washing them.

00:20:34.750 --> 00:20:36.480
That's because the boss
has very high standards

00:20:36.480 --> 00:20:37.200
for hygiene.

00:20:37.200 --> 00:20:37.750
Got it.

00:20:37.750 --> 00:20:38.400
Rinse thoroughly.

00:20:38.400 --> 00:20:38.790
No problem.

00:20:38.790 --> 00:20:39.200
Good.

00:20:39.830 --> 00:20:41.260
By the way, your uniform

00:20:41.280 --> 00:20:42.370
and apron

00:20:42.480 --> 00:20:43.980
are down there. Put them on.

00:20:43.980 --> 00:20:44.660
Okay.

00:20:46.240 --> 00:20:46.790
Mr. Qu,

00:20:47.080 --> 00:20:49.080
another dish of twice-cooked pork.

00:20:49.390 --> 00:20:49.870
Got it.

00:20:49.890 --> 00:20:50.720
A dish of twice-cooked pork again.

00:20:50.720 --> 00:20:52.250
Let me introduce her to you.

00:20:52.510 --> 00:20:53.350
She's Yun,

00:20:53.370 --> 00:20:54.620
also from the Northeast.

00:20:54.620 --> 00:20:55.640
Also from the Northeast?

00:20:55.640 --> 00:20:57.420
We're like a family
from the Northeast then, aren't we?

00:20:57.420 --> 00:20:58.340
She's my girlfriend.

00:20:58.340 --> 00:20:59.070
That's nice.

00:21:01.440 --> 00:21:02.240
Here it comes,

00:21:02.240 --> 00:21:03.270
Mapo Tofu.

00:21:05.300 --> 00:21:06.400
Oh, my feet...

00:21:06.510 --> 00:21:07.640
You nailed it.

00:21:09.070 --> 00:21:11.960
How do we make international calls here?

00:21:12.510 --> 00:21:13.570
For international calls,

00:21:13.570 --> 00:21:15.230
you need to buy a calling card.

00:21:15.360 --> 00:21:17.390
International calls cost less with it.

00:21:17.390 --> 00:21:19.850
Is the rate the same for calling
back to China

00:21:20.180 --> 00:21:22.010
and to France?

00:21:22.040 --> 00:21:23.570
Calling France costs more.

00:21:24.200 --> 00:21:24.750
W-Why do you ask?

00:21:24.750 --> 00:21:26.290
Do you have a friend in France?

00:21:26.290 --> 00:21:27.620
My girlfriend is there.

00:21:27.940 --> 00:21:29.210
I came to Japan

00:21:29.500 --> 00:21:31.340
to work and earn money,

00:21:31.480 --> 00:21:32.750
so I can finally reach France.

00:21:32.750 --> 00:21:34.310
Japan is not my final destination.

00:21:34.310 --> 00:21:36.110
I didn't know you're such a romantic

00:21:36.110 --> 00:21:38.070
who's willing to go through
so much trouble.

00:21:38.070 --> 00:21:39.030
What romantic?

00:21:39.030 --> 00:21:41.590
Aren't I just risking it all for love?

00:21:42.590 --> 00:21:44.720
Right.
You do have to make international calls.

00:21:44.720 --> 00:21:46.560
You can borrow my card tonight.

00:21:46.830 --> 00:21:48.330
I'll take you to buy one when I have time.

00:21:48.330 --> 00:21:49.320
Y-You have such a card?

00:21:49.320 --> 00:21:50.080
Yes, I do.

00:21:51.200 --> 00:21:52.200
I-I'll use yours for now.

00:21:52.200 --> 00:21:52.920
W-When I get paid,

00:21:52.920 --> 00:21:53.960
I'll buy one and reimburse you.

00:21:53.960 --> 00:21:55.290
Don't worry about that.

00:22:12.960 --> 00:22:13.510
Look.

00:22:16.880 --> 00:22:19.000
Are these figures you and your girlfriend?

00:22:19.000 --> 00:22:20.400
My girlfriend drew this.

00:22:20.790 --> 00:22:23.270
She studies architectural design.

00:22:23.510 --> 00:22:26.040
This painting shows
the two of us in Shanghai.

00:22:26.270 --> 00:22:27.400
Good for you.

00:22:28.920 --> 00:22:30.320
This is your girlfriend?

00:22:32.110 --> 00:22:33.240
What a pretty girl.

00:22:33.240 --> 00:22:34.240
She is, isn't she?

00:22:34.270 --> 00:22:34.750
Such a perfect match.

00:22:34.750 --> 00:22:35.510
-She's so beautiful.
-Perfect match.

00:22:35.510 --> 00:22:37.640
She and I grew up together.

00:22:37.840 --> 00:22:39.570
We're childhood sweethearts.

00:22:39.850 --> 00:22:40.870
How very nice.

00:23:05.960 --> 00:23:06.360
Hello?

00:23:06.500 --> 00:23:07.300
Hey, Xiaodan.

00:23:07.920 --> 00:23:08.480
It's me.

00:23:09.070 --> 00:23:10.110
How are you?

00:23:10.180 --> 00:23:11.310
Is everything going well?

00:23:11.310 --> 00:23:12.710
I'm doing very well here.

00:23:12.830 --> 00:23:15.200
I've already worked a full day here today.

00:23:16.480 --> 00:23:18.810
I'm staying at Zhuang Sen's aunt's place.

00:23:19.110 --> 00:23:21.480
She owns a restaurant here.

00:23:21.960 --> 00:23:23.640
I work in it during the day,

00:23:23.640 --> 00:23:25.440
and I sleep at her place at night.

00:23:25.590 --> 00:23:26.880
Some guys here
are also from the Northeast.

00:23:26.880 --> 00:23:27.880
We live together.

00:23:29.760 --> 00:23:31.090
Is this your new number?

00:23:31.440 --> 00:23:32.350
No, it's not.

00:23:32.350 --> 00:23:34.830
J-Just a fellow countryman's.

00:23:35.200 --> 00:23:37.200
I haven't bought a calling card yet.

00:23:37.440 --> 00:23:38.920
I'll let you know when I buy one

00:23:38.920 --> 00:23:40.590
and get a number.

00:23:41.680 --> 00:23:42.330
Oh, right.

00:23:42.640 --> 00:23:44.590
When do you get off work every day?

00:23:44.710 --> 00:23:45.910
When do I get off work?

00:23:46.440 --> 00:23:48.210
About 7 or 8 p.m.

00:23:48.350 --> 00:23:50.500
Sometimes it runs late,
and I'll be off at a bit over 9 p.m.

00:23:50.500 --> 00:23:51.360
How about this?

00:23:51.590 --> 00:23:53.900
Every Sunday night after you get off work,

00:23:53.900 --> 00:23:55.230
let's talk on the phone.

00:23:55.270 --> 00:23:57.030
It happens to be noon here at that time.

00:23:57.030 --> 00:23:59.360
Okay. It'll be more convenient once I have

00:23:59.440 --> 00:24:01.170
my own calling card and number.

00:24:01.200 --> 00:24:03.730
Then we can phone each other
whenever we want.

00:24:04.930 --> 00:24:06.440
I'm waiting for you in France.

00:24:06.440 --> 00:24:07.200
Be patient.

00:24:07.240 --> 00:24:08.970
I'll be with you in France soon.

00:24:10.830 --> 00:24:12.480
Alright, I'm hanging up now.

00:24:16.590 --> 00:24:17.200
Gosh!

00:24:18.090 --> 00:24:18.880
What are you doing?

00:24:18.880 --> 00:24:20.510
What am I doing?
You're staying up at night.

00:24:20.510 --> 00:24:21.500
What are you doing?

00:24:21.500 --> 00:24:22.630
Nothing. I...

00:24:22.720 --> 00:24:24.640
I was just talking to my girlfriend
on the phone.

00:24:24.640 --> 00:24:26.240
She's abroad,
so there's a time difference.

00:24:26.240 --> 00:24:28.350
I don't care who you'd love to call.

00:24:28.350 --> 00:24:30.720
Just don't disturb others' sleep, okay?

00:24:31.850 --> 00:24:33.050
Okay.

00:24:39.480 --> 00:24:40.680
Excuse me. Excuse me!

00:24:41.480 --> 00:24:42.110
Excuse me.

00:24:46.270 --> 00:24:47.730
Thank you for the service.

00:24:49.000 --> 00:24:49.480
Yes.

00:24:49.590 --> 00:24:51.050
Thank you for the service.

00:24:51.270 --> 00:24:53.030
Check, please.

00:24:57.590 --> 00:24:58.990
You'd like to order more?

00:24:59.500 --> 00:25:00.910
No, no, no.

00:25:01.640 --> 00:25:03.000
Check, please.

00:25:03.000 --> 00:25:05.400
J-J-Just a moment.

00:25:05.780 --> 00:25:06.430
Ma'am!

00:25:07.000 --> 00:25:07.510
Ma'am.

00:25:07.940 --> 00:25:10.200
Come here. I don't know what he's saying.

00:25:12.570 --> 00:25:13.170
What?

00:25:14.880 --> 00:25:16.270
Pardon me.

00:25:16.450 --> 00:25:18.900
He's new to the restaurant.

00:25:19.550 --> 00:25:20.510
Sorry.

00:25:21.440 --> 00:25:22.960
I see. I get it now.

00:25:23.350 --> 00:25:25.070
It's okay.

00:25:25.590 --> 00:25:27.110
How may I help you?

00:25:27.440 --> 00:25:29.070
I'd like to get the check.

00:25:29.350 --> 00:25:29.920
Sure.

00:25:29.960 --> 00:25:30.850
Just a moment.

00:25:30.880 --> 00:25:31.880
Okay. Thanks.

00:25:32.000 --> 00:25:32.920
Don't just stand there.

00:25:32.920 --> 00:25:34.920
Fetch the check from the front desk.

00:25:35.050 --> 00:25:36.650
-Got it.
-He's asking for it.

00:25:38.350 --> 00:25:39.110
I'm terribly sorry.

00:25:39.110 --> 00:25:39.550
No worries.

00:25:39.550 --> 00:25:40.790
How was the food?

00:25:41.310 --> 00:25:42.680
The dumplings were delicious.

00:25:42.680 --> 00:25:43.720
Very tasty.

00:25:43.830 --> 00:25:44.550
Yes.

00:25:44.550 --> 00:25:45.680
Delectable, right?

00:25:48.310 --> 00:25:49.240
Give me a second.

00:25:52.410 --> 00:25:53.240
Here you go.

00:25:53.270 --> 00:25:54.580
Thank you very much.

00:25:54.610 --> 00:25:55.880
Thank you for the service.

00:25:55.880 --> 00:25:57.110
Let's go.

00:25:58.030 --> 00:25:59.510
We hope to see you again.

00:25:59.640 --> 00:26:00.590
You surely will.

00:26:00.830 --> 00:26:02.240
Thank you so much.

00:26:02.480 --> 00:26:03.270
Take care.

00:26:03.470 --> 00:26:03.970
This way.

00:26:03.970 --> 00:26:04.500
Let's go.

00:26:07.780 --> 00:26:09.390
I'm truly sorry.

00:26:11.960 --> 00:26:13.350
Thank you very much!

00:26:18.630 --> 00:26:20.360
I didn't get what he was saying.

00:26:22.220 --> 00:26:23.830
Are you not going to learn Japanese,

00:26:23.830 --> 00:26:25.290
or are you just incapable?

00:26:25.920 --> 00:26:26.980
It's not like that.

00:26:27.510 --> 00:26:29.200
You didn't say
I'd have to serve customers.

00:26:29.200 --> 00:26:31.610
So I figured
I didn't need to learn Japanese.

00:26:31.610 --> 00:26:32.810
Do you hear yourself?

00:26:34.240 --> 00:26:35.750
Look, you are in Japan now,

00:26:35.750 --> 00:26:37.880
yet you can't speak a word of Japanese.

00:26:38.680 --> 00:26:40.540
I-I just thought I should hurry up

00:26:40.640 --> 00:26:42.550
and learn French instead.

00:26:42.550 --> 00:26:44.350
I'm currently learning French.

00:26:44.690 --> 00:26:46.480
I don't care
if you're going to France or not.

00:26:46.480 --> 00:26:48.550
As long as you work here,
you must learn Japanese!

00:26:48.550 --> 00:26:51.350
You should at least
understand the basics, right?

00:26:51.440 --> 00:26:52.110
Like "hello,"

00:26:52.110 --> 00:26:52.880
"thank you,"

00:26:53.110 --> 00:26:53.920
"sorry,"

00:26:55.160 --> 00:26:56.030
and "check."

00:26:56.640 --> 00:26:57.260
Right.

00:26:57.280 --> 00:26:59.010
You must begin learning it now.

00:26:59.070 --> 00:26:59.480
Yes!

00:26:59.740 --> 00:27:00.240
What?

00:27:00.480 --> 00:27:00.960
"Yes."

00:27:02.000 --> 00:27:03.070
A-Aren't I speaking Japanese?

00:27:03.070 --> 00:27:03.440
"Yes!"

00:27:03.440 --> 00:27:04.770
I saw it on TV yesterday.

00:27:04.770 --> 00:27:06.110
I learned the word for "punk."

00:27:06.110 --> 00:27:07.680
Then another man said "yes."

00:27:07.680 --> 00:27:08.510
Isn't that Japanese?

00:27:08.510 --> 00:27:09.640
Cut it out.

00:27:13.350 --> 00:27:14.460
Are you kidding me?

00:27:15.220 --> 00:27:16.080
What's that now?

00:27:16.080 --> 00:27:17.280
"Are you kidding me?"

00:27:19.390 --> 00:27:20.320
Clean the table.

00:27:20.320 --> 00:27:20.750
Yes.

00:27:20.780 --> 00:27:21.320
Make it quick.

00:27:21.320 --> 00:27:21.660
Yes!

00:27:23.670 --> 00:27:25.400
You little fool.

00:27:31.830 --> 00:27:33.070
I've checked the plumbing and wiring.

00:27:33.070 --> 00:27:34.800
Everything should be fine now.

00:27:35.750 --> 00:27:36.790
Are you done with the tidying up?

00:27:36.790 --> 00:27:37.830
Yes, almost.

00:27:40.110 --> 00:27:41.170
Just this last bit.

00:27:51.960 --> 00:27:53.740
Auntie, greetings.

00:27:54.000 --> 00:27:56.310
Xiaoman is in Japan.
He called and said he is doing well.

00:27:56.310 --> 00:27:57.750
But he always tells the good news
and hides the bad.

00:27:57.750 --> 00:27:59.210
Do watch over him, Auntie.

00:27:59.480 --> 00:28:02.010
I believe he can sense your blessings
for him.

00:28:02.880 --> 00:28:04.440
I wish him all the best.

00:28:06.240 --> 00:28:07.840
What are you mumbling about?

00:28:08.140 --> 00:28:11.330
I thought I'd tell Xiaoman's grandma
that he had gone abroad.

00:28:11.330 --> 00:28:12.640
Given the time difference,

00:28:12.640 --> 00:28:15.360
I'm afraid she might visit his dreams
at the wrong time.

00:28:15.360 --> 00:28:17.270
K-Keep talking to her then.

00:28:17.360 --> 00:28:18.960
Lots of workers have retired

00:28:20.240 --> 00:28:21.440
from the factory now.

00:28:21.910 --> 00:28:24.000
Some took a severance package,
and some are on unpaid leave.

00:28:24.000 --> 00:28:26.200
Many others are sick. They've all left.

00:28:27.160 --> 00:28:28.220
But we won't leave.

00:28:29.110 --> 00:28:30.570
We're not going anywhere.

00:28:30.590 --> 00:28:31.440
We'll stick around and wait for

00:28:31.440 --> 00:28:32.500
Xiaoman's return.

00:28:32.510 --> 00:28:33.160
Don't worry.

00:28:33.160 --> 00:28:33.880
Rest easy.

00:28:38.150 --> 00:28:38.630
Wait.

00:28:39.140 --> 00:28:40.130
I'd like to say a few words too.

00:28:40.130 --> 00:28:40.760
Go ahead.

00:28:45.200 --> 00:28:46.330
Xiaoman's grandma,

00:28:47.160 --> 00:28:49.510
please watch over Xiaoman from heaven.

00:28:50.680 --> 00:28:52.340
We'll take care of the family.

00:28:52.590 --> 00:28:55.400
C-Can I tell her that thing?

00:28:55.920 --> 00:28:57.640
Just say it. I've told her already.

00:28:57.640 --> 00:28:58.880
It can't be hidden anyway.

00:28:58.880 --> 00:29:01.400
The factory hasn't been doing as well
over these years.

00:29:01.400 --> 00:29:03.110
Many of the old folks had no choice

00:29:03.110 --> 00:29:04.960
but to move to another place.

00:29:04.980 --> 00:29:05.980
Did you know that?

00:29:06.550 --> 00:29:07.950
We were also planning...

00:29:11.050 --> 00:29:12.450
But we won't go anywhere.

00:29:12.480 --> 00:29:14.110
I'll keep the house clean

00:29:14.350 --> 00:29:16.720
so Xiaoman can stay here
whenever he wants.

00:29:16.720 --> 00:29:18.420
I've said all that to her already.

00:29:18.420 --> 00:29:20.750
-You've said all that?
-Yes, everything.

00:29:21.000 --> 00:29:21.800
Alright then.

00:29:23.270 --> 00:29:25.070
May you bless our child Xiaoman.

00:29:25.160 --> 00:29:25.690
Alright.

00:29:26.310 --> 00:29:26.960
Cover it up.

00:29:26.960 --> 00:29:27.790
It's time to go.

00:29:27.790 --> 00:29:29.120
-Sure.
-Let's cover it.

00:29:31.010 --> 00:29:31.870
Give me the bag.

00:29:33.720 --> 00:29:34.550
I'll carry that.

00:29:34.550 --> 00:29:35.200
Just keep walking.

00:29:35.200 --> 00:29:36.590
I'll turn off the lights. Hurry.

00:29:36.590 --> 00:29:37.250
Be careful.

00:29:37.400 --> 00:29:37.830
Okay.

00:29:43.680 --> 00:29:47.170
"Are you... kidding..."

00:29:51.720 --> 00:29:53.400
The stewed beans smell amazing.

00:29:53.400 --> 00:29:55.600
It feels like I'm back in the Northeast.

00:29:55.750 --> 00:29:57.010
I-I'd like to taste it.

00:29:57.110 --> 00:29:58.770
What are you muttering about?

00:29:59.310 --> 00:30:01.400
The boss said something to me in Japanese
yesterday.

00:30:01.400 --> 00:30:02.510
She asked me to learn the language.

00:30:02.510 --> 00:30:04.240
I've forgotten what she said.

00:30:05.070 --> 00:30:08.110
It was something like "kidding..."

00:30:09.880 --> 00:30:10.880
What is he saying?

00:30:11.030 --> 00:30:11.830
I have no idea.

00:30:13.070 --> 00:30:14.160
She said something like

00:30:14.160 --> 00:30:15.550
"are you...

00:30:15.550 --> 00:30:16.590
kidding..."

00:30:16.790 --> 00:30:18.550
"Are you kidding me?"

00:30:18.550 --> 00:30:19.160
Was that it?

00:30:19.160 --> 00:30:20.290
What does that mean?

00:30:20.710 --> 00:30:21.910
She was scolding you.

00:30:23.150 --> 00:30:23.880
Scolding me?

00:30:24.000 --> 00:30:24.930
Pretty harshly.

00:30:25.900 --> 00:30:27.500
What was she saying about me?

00:30:27.640 --> 00:30:28.240
No.

00:30:28.240 --> 00:30:30.550
If you got that from Madam Zhuang,

00:30:30.550 --> 00:30:32.080
it was actually quite nice.

00:30:32.590 --> 00:30:34.100
She was basically saying, "cut it out."

00:30:34.100 --> 00:30:35.430
T-That was kind of nice.

00:30:35.510 --> 00:30:36.480
She scolded you.

00:30:36.480 --> 00:30:38.540
What are you only asking about it now?

00:30:38.680 --> 00:30:41.030
That's because I couldn't remember
how she said it yesterday.

00:30:41.030 --> 00:30:42.030
Food's ready.

00:30:42.110 --> 00:30:42.910
Here it comes.

00:30:44.270 --> 00:30:45.350
Authentic flavor.

00:30:45.350 --> 00:30:46.510
Original taste.

00:30:46.510 --> 00:30:47.110
Smells amazing, huh?

00:30:47.110 --> 00:30:48.750
Northeast-style stewed beans.

00:30:48.750 --> 00:30:50.080
Let me get you some rice.

00:30:50.480 --> 00:30:51.400
Okay. Thanks.

00:30:51.940 --> 00:30:54.180
"Thank you very much."

00:30:54.400 --> 00:30:55.110
"Dinner is served."

00:30:55.110 --> 00:30:55.920
"Eat up, please."

00:30:55.920 --> 00:30:56.750
Come on, don't just sit there.

00:30:56.750 --> 00:30:57.640
Let's dig in!

00:30:57.640 --> 00:31:01.000
"I-I-I..."

00:31:02.810 --> 00:31:04.010
Not a word is correct.

00:31:04.030 --> 00:31:04.590
Let's eat.

00:31:04.590 --> 00:31:06.590
"Please wait a moment."

00:31:06.880 --> 00:31:10.440
"I... I am..."

00:31:10.640 --> 00:31:12.260
-Stop talking gibberish.
-Eat up.

00:31:12.260 --> 00:31:13.180
Eat it

00:31:13.590 --> 00:31:14.450
while it's hot.

00:31:14.720 --> 00:31:15.400
Oh my god.

00:31:16.340 --> 00:31:18.400
D-Did you not spare some for the boss?

00:31:19.270 --> 00:31:20.590
Look at him, look.

00:31:20.590 --> 00:31:21.680
Not socially savvy at all.

00:31:21.680 --> 00:31:22.510
I brought these dried beans

00:31:22.510 --> 00:31:24.130
from home.
How can we not spare some for the boss?

00:31:24.130 --> 00:31:24.920
It'll upset her, right?

00:31:24.920 --> 00:31:25.880
What are you going to do?

00:31:25.880 --> 00:31:27.410
I'll bring some to the boss.

00:31:27.750 --> 00:31:28.550
He wants to be scolded.

00:31:28.550 --> 00:31:29.510
So you're the expert now.

00:31:29.510 --> 00:31:30.910
He's about to be scolded.

00:31:39.030 --> 00:31:39.590
Boss?

00:31:41.510 --> 00:31:42.070
Boss?

00:31:42.510 --> 00:31:43.110
Come in.

00:31:45.580 --> 00:31:46.180
Boss.

00:31:48.350 --> 00:31:51.750
H-Here's a dish made of the dried beans
I brought from home.

00:31:52.030 --> 00:31:52.720
Try some.

00:31:52.720 --> 00:31:53.880
Don't eat pickles all the time.

00:31:53.880 --> 00:31:55.410
Y-You need some nutrition.

00:31:55.440 --> 00:31:56.160
Thank you.

00:31:56.830 --> 00:32:00.200
Well, I've been here for a long time,
right?

00:32:01.110 --> 00:32:02.710
My stomach isn't quite well.

00:32:03.100 --> 00:32:05.450
This is too greasy
for my system to digest.

00:32:06.360 --> 00:32:07.090
Take it away.

00:32:07.150 --> 00:32:09.550
You don't usually eat this stuff, right?

00:32:09.550 --> 00:32:10.070
Right.

00:32:11.400 --> 00:32:14.160
What a shame.

00:32:15.650 --> 00:32:17.680
It's from home. J-Just keep some.

00:32:17.710 --> 00:32:19.470
K-Keep some for yourself.

00:32:19.960 --> 00:32:20.830
Put it here. Right on the side.

00:32:20.830 --> 00:32:21.550
G-get some.

00:32:22.030 --> 00:32:22.480
Just a little.

00:32:22.480 --> 00:32:23.960
I'm not asking you to eat a lot.

00:32:23.960 --> 00:32:24.880
That'll upset your stomach.

00:32:24.880 --> 00:32:26.510
But a couple of pieces won't hurt.

00:32:26.510 --> 00:32:27.000
Okay.

00:32:27.350 --> 00:32:28.110
Good.

00:32:28.110 --> 00:32:29.310
I won't leave you the meat then.

00:32:29.310 --> 00:32:30.590
J-Just have some beans.

00:32:30.590 --> 00:32:31.400
Thank you.

00:32:52.630 --> 00:32:53.540
Look, Guoqing.

00:32:53.790 --> 00:32:55.650
Xiaodan is doing quite well here.

00:32:55.830 --> 00:32:57.920
Seems like she has adapted
to living in France.

00:32:57.920 --> 00:32:59.150
That's a relief for me.

00:32:59.150 --> 00:33:01.350
I've fulfilled my duty to your parents.

00:33:01.820 --> 00:33:02.950
Besides, recently,

00:33:03.200 --> 00:33:04.790
I've finally understood this saying,

00:33:04.790 --> 00:33:06.270
"Looking is not seeing."

00:33:06.830 --> 00:33:08.490
In the past, I did stand high up

00:33:08.720 --> 00:33:10.070
and see far into the distance.

00:33:10.070 --> 00:33:10.750
But now,

00:33:10.750 --> 00:33:12.790
I'm actually in this spot.

00:33:13.680 --> 00:33:16.160
Xiaodan, when is your boyfriend coming?

00:33:17.510 --> 00:33:18.310
Very soon.

00:33:18.590 --> 00:33:19.750
He's currently in Japan.

00:33:19.750 --> 00:33:22.410
I think he can come meet me in France
before long.

00:33:23.480 --> 00:33:25.160
My happiest moment every month

00:33:25.160 --> 00:33:26.790
is when I count my salary.

00:33:29.460 --> 00:33:30.720
Why not let me help you count yours?

00:33:30.720 --> 00:33:31.980
No need. I can figure it out.

00:33:31.980 --> 00:33:33.030
C-Counting these notes

00:33:33.030 --> 00:33:34.590
is not exactly a pleasure.

00:33:34.590 --> 00:33:35.790
Before I realize it,

00:33:35.790 --> 00:33:36.750
I've counted up to 10,000.

00:33:36.750 --> 00:33:37.350
T-There's

00:33:37.350 --> 00:33:39.080
no thrill in counting the cash.

00:33:39.270 --> 00:33:40.240
When I save enough money,

00:33:40.240 --> 00:33:42.030
I'll go back home
and run a small business.

00:33:42.030 --> 00:33:43.480
You want to be a boss?
Just keep chopping food.

00:33:43.480 --> 00:33:44.160
Dream on.

00:33:44.940 --> 00:33:47.540
Will I still be chopping food
if I become a boss?

00:33:47.590 --> 00:33:49.790
What now? You're such a pain in the neck!

00:33:51.400 --> 00:33:53.250
W-Who is our boss quarreling with?

00:33:53.250 --> 00:33:54.000
Please leave.

00:33:54.000 --> 00:33:54.590
Let's go take a look.

00:33:54.590 --> 00:33:55.390
Mr. Watanabe.

00:33:59.170 --> 00:34:00.960
How many times do I have to tell you?

00:34:00.960 --> 00:34:01.890
What is it, Boss?

00:34:04.440 --> 00:34:05.160
Ms. Zhuang,

00:34:05.190 --> 00:34:07.450
Mr. Maeda's name alone is a money-maker.

00:34:07.550 --> 00:34:09.150
By just authorizing us to use

00:34:09.230 --> 00:34:11.290
his gold belt, trophies, and medals,

00:34:11.510 --> 00:34:13.760
you'll get paid without lifting a finger.

00:34:13.760 --> 00:34:14.840
Mr. Watanabe,

00:34:16.000 --> 00:34:18.070
I'll say this one last time.

00:34:18.179 --> 00:34:19.429
Maeda is dead.

00:34:20.150 --> 00:34:22.239
I'd hate to have him connected

00:34:22.270 --> 00:34:24.469
with kickboxing anymore.

00:34:27.070 --> 00:34:28.440
The honors Mr. Maeda received
when he was alive

00:34:28.440 --> 00:34:29.840
can bring greater value.

00:34:30.040 --> 00:34:31.440
Why waste them?

00:34:31.590 --> 00:34:33.550
You are causing us trouble now.

00:34:34.230 --> 00:34:35.310
Please leave.

00:34:35.790 --> 00:34:36.350
Right?

00:34:38.530 --> 00:34:39.449
Our...

00:34:39.730 --> 00:34:41.989
Our boss wants you out.

00:34:42.969 --> 00:34:43.449
Leave.

00:34:43.630 --> 00:34:44.000
That way.

00:34:44.000 --> 00:34:44.670
Go. Let's go.

00:34:44.670 --> 00:34:46.400
This matter is between Ms. Zhuang and me.

00:34:46.400 --> 00:34:48.360
You'd better not butt in.

00:34:48.440 --> 00:34:49.610
This is futile,
since I don't understand a word.

00:34:49.610 --> 00:34:50.170
Leave!

00:34:50.320 --> 00:34:51.580
-Go away.
-Ms. Zhuang,

00:34:52.030 --> 00:34:53.510
we're both from Tiecheng.

00:34:53.920 --> 00:34:55.550
Compared to other Chinese people,

00:34:55.550 --> 00:34:57.680
we are closer fellow townsmen, right?

00:34:58.110 --> 00:35:00.400
Don't you think it's nice
for fellow townsmen

00:35:00.400 --> 00:35:01.920
to help each other and make money

00:35:01.920 --> 00:35:03.450
from foreigners together?

00:35:03.840 --> 00:35:05.100
You're from Tiecheng?

00:35:05.800 --> 00:35:06.590
Shut up.

00:35:09.050 --> 00:35:11.040
All that stuff about Tiecheng and Maeda

00:35:11.040 --> 00:35:12.200
is in the past.

00:35:13.550 --> 00:35:14.280
See them out.

00:35:14.480 --> 00:35:14.960
Right.

00:35:15.070 --> 00:35:16.510
Tiecheng or whatever doesn't work today.

00:35:16.510 --> 00:35:17.030
Please leave

00:35:17.030 --> 00:35:17.970
before our boss gets mad.

00:35:17.970 --> 00:35:18.700
Get a move on.

00:35:19.150 --> 00:35:19.880
Young fellow...

00:35:19.880 --> 00:35:20.590
-Hands off.
-Talk some sense

00:35:20.590 --> 00:35:21.670
into your boss for me.

00:35:21.670 --> 00:35:22.760
Our boss might really get mad.

00:35:22.760 --> 00:35:23.620
J-Just go away.

00:35:23.840 --> 00:35:24.550
-Sir, please leave.
-See them off.

00:35:24.550 --> 00:35:25.400
That way, go.

00:35:25.400 --> 00:35:25.840
Please.

00:35:25.840 --> 00:35:26.550
Hurry and go away.

00:35:26.550 --> 00:35:28.080
Be quick. No more dawdling.

00:35:28.550 --> 00:35:29.230
Ms. Zhuang,

00:35:29.780 --> 00:35:32.240
please do take my offer
into consideration.

00:35:32.470 --> 00:35:33.400
I'll be back.

00:35:39.090 --> 00:35:39.610
Guo,

00:35:41.020 --> 00:35:41.750
who are they?

00:35:41.870 --> 00:35:42.930
Are you okay, Boss?

00:35:43.190 --> 00:35:43.710
G-Give me some space.

00:35:43.710 --> 00:35:44.920
Quick, go inside.

00:35:44.940 --> 00:35:46.190
My stomach's acting up again from anger.

00:35:46.190 --> 00:35:46.760
What's going on?

00:35:46.760 --> 00:35:47.760
Get me some warm water.

00:35:47.760 --> 00:35:48.360
A stomachache?

00:35:48.360 --> 00:35:49.230
I'll get the water.

00:35:49.230 --> 00:35:50.360
Yes, get some water.

00:35:50.510 --> 00:35:51.320
Careful. Slow down.

00:35:51.320 --> 00:35:52.780
That truly infuriated me.

00:35:58.480 --> 00:35:59.030
Boss.

00:35:59.960 --> 00:36:00.510
Come in.

00:36:05.920 --> 00:36:06.590
Boss.

00:36:07.840 --> 00:36:10.550
There happened to be some millet around,

00:36:11.030 --> 00:36:12.690
so I made you porridge with it.

00:36:13.150 --> 00:36:14.030
Back in my hometown,

00:36:14.030 --> 00:36:15.150
people who have stomachaches

00:36:15.150 --> 00:36:15.840
would all eat this.

00:36:15.840 --> 00:36:17.040
It works like a charm,

00:36:17.110 --> 00:36:18.570
as it soothes the stomach.

00:36:18.720 --> 00:36:19.510
Thank you.

00:36:20.000 --> 00:36:20.550
Eat it, Boss.

00:36:20.550 --> 00:36:21.070
Let me know

00:36:21.070 --> 00:36:21.550
if this is not enough.

00:36:21.550 --> 00:36:22.700
There's more in the pot.

00:36:22.700 --> 00:36:24.100
I'll leave you to it then.

00:36:24.360 --> 00:36:25.000
Xiaoman.

00:36:29.090 --> 00:36:31.130
At home, Zhuang Sen calls me Auntie.

00:36:32.190 --> 00:36:33.520
You can call me that too.

00:36:35.030 --> 00:36:35.630
That's right.

00:36:35.630 --> 00:36:37.830
That's how we address people back home.

00:36:37.920 --> 00:36:38.400
Really.

00:36:38.400 --> 00:36:40.530
I call all my friends' aunts "Auntie" too.

00:36:40.530 --> 00:36:41.850
This custom should be observed here too.

00:36:41.850 --> 00:36:43.180
It feels closer, right?

00:36:44.210 --> 00:36:46.640
You can only call me that here,

00:36:48.590 --> 00:36:50.230
not in the restaurant.

00:36:50.510 --> 00:36:51.370
Keep it in mind.

00:36:52.550 --> 00:36:53.750
Just in private then.

00:36:54.360 --> 00:36:55.160
Okay, I got it.

00:36:55.210 --> 00:36:56.590
I'm leaving then, Auntie.

00:36:56.590 --> 00:36:57.550
Let me know if you need anything.

00:36:57.550 --> 00:36:57.960
Okay.

00:36:58.510 --> 00:36:59.230
Thank you!

00:36:59.700 --> 00:37:00.700
Don't mention it.

00:37:07.230 --> 00:37:08.450
Hello, I'm Meng Ge.

00:37:08.480 --> 00:37:09.610
Did you ask to see me?

00:37:11.070 --> 00:37:12.000
Xia Lei?

00:37:12.110 --> 00:37:13.360
Long time no see, Meng Ge.

00:37:13.360 --> 00:37:14.360
What brings you here?

00:37:14.360 --> 00:37:16.220
Sit. What would you like to drink?

00:37:16.250 --> 00:37:16.930
Americano.

00:37:20.430 --> 00:37:21.950
I heard from Xiaodan

00:37:22.280 --> 00:37:24.590
that you started a business
and your partner screwed you?

00:37:24.590 --> 00:37:25.110
Yes.

00:37:25.230 --> 00:37:26.480
I paid a price,

00:37:26.500 --> 00:37:28.030
yet the lesson was worth it.

00:37:28.440 --> 00:37:30.100
What did you come to see me for?

00:37:31.920 --> 00:37:34.110
I hope you can recommend me to Fenlier.

00:37:34.960 --> 00:37:35.840
You know,

00:37:35.840 --> 00:37:38.000
I majored in Communication Engineering

00:37:38.000 --> 00:37:39.480
and minored in Finance in college.

00:37:39.480 --> 00:37:40.940
I am exactly
the kind of interdisciplinary talents

00:37:40.940 --> 00:37:42.510
that your company is seeking.

00:37:42.510 --> 00:37:45.110
You did some research on Fenlier
before coming here?

00:37:45.110 --> 00:37:47.710
How else would I have figured out
you work here?

00:37:47.760 --> 00:37:50.220
But why should I help you get a job
in Fenlier?

00:37:50.320 --> 00:37:52.480
The Strategic Investment Department
you're in

00:37:52.480 --> 00:37:53.760
was just set up.

00:37:53.760 --> 00:37:54.710
If you're looking for

00:37:54.710 --> 00:37:56.030
an excellent working partner,

00:37:56.030 --> 00:37:57.440
then I'm the best choice.

00:37:57.440 --> 00:37:58.300
Think about it.

00:37:58.760 --> 00:38:00.550
We both came from the East Chemical Plant,

00:38:00.550 --> 00:38:01.800
and we know a lot about each other.

00:38:01.800 --> 00:38:03.260
Plus, I'll never harm you.

00:38:03.440 --> 00:38:04.840
Even if you intend to,

00:38:05.320 --> 00:38:06.360
I won't be afraid.

00:38:07.490 --> 00:38:08.180
Also,

00:38:09.550 --> 00:38:12.550
I know employees here get cash rewards

00:38:12.550 --> 00:38:14.360
for recommending talents.

00:38:14.960 --> 00:38:17.160
Why let someone else earn that money?

00:38:19.320 --> 00:38:20.440
Do you really think

00:38:21.030 --> 00:38:23.560
you can be
an outstanding investment banker?

00:38:23.840 --> 00:38:24.960
You've done some research,

00:38:24.960 --> 00:38:27.400
so I believe you're aware
of our corporate culture—

00:38:27.400 --> 00:38:28.600
wolf-like ferocity.

00:38:32.510 --> 00:38:33.320
I'm ready.

00:38:33.920 --> 00:38:35.070
The way you push up your glasses

00:38:35.070 --> 00:38:36.900
still makes you look like a student.

00:38:36.900 --> 00:38:37.840
I really can't imagine

00:38:37.840 --> 00:38:39.760
what you'd be like as a wolf.

00:38:43.630 --> 00:38:44.190
Fine.

00:38:44.760 --> 00:38:45.880
I'll help you.

00:38:47.710 --> 00:38:48.320
Thanks.

00:38:53.670 --> 00:38:54.480
Excuse me.

00:38:57.150 --> 00:38:58.110
Excuse me!

00:39:06.890 --> 00:39:07.960
The boss is not here.

00:39:07.960 --> 00:39:10.070
What does her absence have to do with me?

00:39:10.070 --> 00:39:11.320
I'm not asking to see her.

00:39:11.320 --> 00:39:12.670
I'm here to eat.

00:39:12.760 --> 00:39:13.760
I'll get the menu.

00:39:14.190 --> 00:39:15.320
Hold on. Not so fast.

00:39:17.670 --> 00:39:19.800
I'm your only customer here, aren't I?

00:39:20.420 --> 00:39:21.440
Chat with me for a bit.

00:39:21.440 --> 00:39:22.400
What's there to chat about?

00:39:22.400 --> 00:39:23.590
I don't have a say in the boss's affairs.

00:39:23.590 --> 00:39:25.920
I understand why you did what you did
that day.

00:39:25.920 --> 00:39:27.510
We're both working for others.

00:39:27.510 --> 00:39:28.590
You stood up for your boss,

00:39:28.590 --> 00:39:30.110
and I had to do my job for mine.

00:39:30.110 --> 00:39:32.510
But my visit today
is not about that matter.

00:39:33.440 --> 00:39:34.360
What do you want then?

00:39:34.360 --> 00:39:36.400
Can't I just come over
to make friends with you?

00:39:36.400 --> 00:39:37.190
No way, sir.

00:39:37.190 --> 00:39:38.320
You want to make friends with me?

00:39:38.320 --> 00:39:40.180
Is there a point of doing so at all?

00:39:40.510 --> 00:39:42.370
Based on what you said that day...

00:39:42.510 --> 00:39:44.110
I know Madam Zhuang is from Tiecheng.

00:39:44.110 --> 00:39:45.440
Are you also from there?

00:39:45.710 --> 00:39:46.510
I'm from Tiecheng too.

00:39:46.510 --> 00:39:47.230
I know.

00:39:47.550 --> 00:39:48.000
Which part...

00:39:48.000 --> 00:39:48.960
of Tiecheng are you from?

00:39:48.960 --> 00:39:49.760
Downtown?

00:39:49.810 --> 00:39:51.920
Yeah. I haven't introduced myself yet.

00:39:51.920 --> 00:39:53.180
My name is Yu Qiangbei.

00:39:54.320 --> 00:39:55.120
What's yours?

00:39:55.800 --> 00:39:56.660
Zhang Xiaoman.

00:39:56.920 --> 00:39:57.800
Zhang Xiaoman, huh?

00:39:57.800 --> 00:39:58.590
I'm from

00:39:58.590 --> 00:39:59.880
the East Chemical Plant.

00:39:59.880 --> 00:40:01.630
You're from the East Chemical Plant?

00:40:01.630 --> 00:40:03.150
It really is a small world.

00:40:03.150 --> 00:40:04.840
I used to live right next to this factory.

00:40:04.840 --> 00:40:06.550
-Really?
-I know a lot of people from that factory.

00:40:06.550 --> 00:40:07.960
But I never saw you there.

00:40:08.510 --> 00:40:09.880
I came to Japan a long time ago.

00:40:09.880 --> 00:40:11.810
That was why you never saw me there.

00:40:12.250 --> 00:40:13.050
Do you know...

00:40:13.630 --> 00:40:16.550
why your boss went livid?

00:40:16.960 --> 00:40:19.030
Actually, we all knew her husband.

00:40:19.120 --> 00:40:20.190
He was a Japanese man

00:40:20.190 --> 00:40:21.000
named Maeda.

00:40:21.280 --> 00:40:23.480
He used to be professional boxer
at my boss's place,

00:40:23.480 --> 00:40:24.760
the Watanabe Boxing Gym.

00:40:24.760 --> 00:40:26.110
He won a brutal fight

00:40:26.400 --> 00:40:28.400
and collapsed in the ring from exhaustion.

00:40:28.400 --> 00:40:30.960
Some gamblers who lost big
chased after him.

00:40:30.980 --> 00:40:32.400
He then fell into the sea and died.

00:40:32.400 --> 00:40:33.670
It wasn't our fault.

00:40:33.880 --> 00:40:35.760
But Madam Zhuang got mad at us.

00:40:36.070 --> 00:40:38.000
She hid Maeda's gold belt

00:40:38.190 --> 00:40:39.720
and started hating our gym.

00:40:40.000 --> 00:40:41.660
What did you come to Japan for?

00:40:41.840 --> 00:40:45.360
First, I'm here to make money.

00:40:46.190 --> 00:40:49.070
Second,
I also need an oversea travel record,

00:40:49.190 --> 00:40:51.300
s-since I'm planning to go to France.

00:40:52.000 --> 00:40:53.860
My girlfriend is studying there.

00:40:53.920 --> 00:40:55.180
I'd like to be with her.

00:40:55.780 --> 00:40:56.980
You remind me

00:40:57.010 --> 00:40:59.080
of when I first came to Japan.

00:40:59.760 --> 00:41:01.030
I was just like you now,

00:41:02.400 --> 00:41:04.150
with a stubborn streak

00:41:04.550 --> 00:41:06.350
and a will to never admit defeat.

00:41:06.440 --> 00:41:08.040
I find you admirable.

00:41:09.070 --> 00:41:10.070
And I think you are

00:41:10.070 --> 00:41:11.600
a loyal and devoted person.

00:41:12.230 --> 00:41:13.840
Buddy, this won't do.

00:41:13.950 --> 00:41:15.070
Now that you're in Japan,

00:41:15.070 --> 00:41:16.630
you need to make money like crazy.

00:41:16.630 --> 00:41:18.090
Every second is valuable.

00:41:18.440 --> 00:41:20.590
Why don't I get you a job
in the boxing gym?

00:41:20.590 --> 00:41:22.720
It pays more than waiting tables here.

00:41:25.920 --> 00:41:26.780
Auntie Zhuang.

00:41:26.920 --> 00:41:27.670
Come in!

00:41:33.960 --> 00:41:36.630
Auntie, I need a word with you.

00:41:40.840 --> 00:41:41.970
What is it? Speak up.

00:41:42.590 --> 00:41:44.230
Well, today...

00:41:45.110 --> 00:41:47.070
Yu Qiangbei came to the restaurant.

00:41:47.070 --> 00:41:48.960
He said he'd get me a new job.

00:41:49.510 --> 00:41:51.060
Just ignore whatever those people say.

00:41:51.060 --> 00:41:51.640
Well,

00:41:51.660 --> 00:41:53.790
h-he asked me to work at his boxing gym.

00:41:55.760 --> 00:41:57.020
You and the boxing gym?

00:41:57.800 --> 00:41:59.920
Wait. What can you possibly do there?

00:42:00.150 --> 00:42:02.960
He said my job would be
cleaning up the place,

00:42:02.960 --> 00:42:04.880
and selling drinks

00:42:05.720 --> 00:42:07.450
and stuff at particular times.

00:42:09.670 --> 00:42:10.930
You want to work there?

00:42:11.510 --> 00:42:14.320
I figured I'd be free
after the restaurant's working hours

00:42:14.320 --> 00:42:16.360
at night, and I could make more money
by taking that job

00:42:16.360 --> 00:42:18.560
at his place, since he'd pay me the hour.

00:42:18.760 --> 00:42:20.230
Go work there if you want.

00:42:21.060 --> 00:42:24.180
B-But that day, I saw he

00:42:24.710 --> 00:42:25.590
and you...

00:42:25.590 --> 00:42:27.320
This has nothing to do with you.

00:42:28.070 --> 00:42:29.400
I know you need money.

00:42:30.480 --> 00:42:31.960
Yes, you can make money at his boxing gym.

00:42:31.960 --> 00:42:33.360
The tips are good, right?

00:42:35.880 --> 00:42:39.030
Okay. In my spare time at night,

00:42:39.030 --> 00:42:41.440
I'll work at his place.

00:42:42.640 --> 00:42:45.350
I'll just focus on my job
and ignore anything else.

00:42:45.350 --> 00:42:45.840
Okay.

00:42:46.580 --> 00:42:47.980
Make your own decisions.

00:42:48.710 --> 00:42:50.580
I understand
you're in urgent need of money.

00:42:50.580 --> 00:42:51.430
However,

00:42:53.070 --> 00:42:54.150
don't tell them

00:42:54.200 --> 00:42:55.730
I know about your job there.

00:42:56.320 --> 00:42:57.280
I got it.

00:42:57.920 --> 00:42:58.450
Alright.

00:42:59.360 --> 00:43:00.470
Is there anything else?

00:43:00.470 --> 00:43:02.020
No. Go to bed early, Auntie.